## 5. Sequence Diagrams

### 5.1 Story #1 ‚Äî Message Generation Flow

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    actor User as Student (User)
    participant FE as Frontend (api.js)
    participant BE as Flask app.py
    participant OM as outreach.py
    participant AI as AI Service (mocked P4 / Bedrock P5)
    participant DB as data/ (in-memory)

    User->>FE: Clicks "Get Message Help"<br/>selects recipient, tone, goal
    FE->>BE: POST /api/outreach/generate<br/>{ recipientId, tone, goal, custom_note }
    BE->>DB: get_user_by_id(recipientId)
    DB-->>BE: recipient dict (or None)
    alt recipientId missing
        BE-->>FE: 400 { error: "recipientId is required" }
    else recipient not found
        BE-->>FE: 404 { error: "User N not found" }
    else valid request
        BE->>OM: generate_outreach_message(sender, recipient, context)
        OM->>AI: _call_ai(prompt)
        AI-->>OM: draft string (mock: template expansion)
        OM-->>BE: { draft, char_count, tone, tips, alternatives }
        BE-->>FE: 200 { draft, char_count, tone, tips, alternatives }
        FE-->>User: Displays draft + tips in UI
    end
```

### 5.2 Story #7 ‚Äî Readiness Check Flow

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    actor User as Job Seeker (User)
    participant FE as Frontend (api.js)
    participant BE as Flask app.py
    participant OM as outreach.py
    participant DB as data/ (in-memory)

    User->>FE: Navigates to "Message Someone"
    FE->>BE: GET /api/outreach/readiness
    BE->>DB: resolve user (CURRENT_USER or userId param)
    DB-->>BE: user dict (or None)
    alt userId provided but not found
        BE-->>FE: 404 { error: "User N not found" }
    else user resolved
        BE->>OM: compute_outreach_readiness(user)
        OM->>OM: Run 9 evaluator lambdas
        OM-->>BE: { score, max_score, level, breakdown, top_tips, can_message }
        BE-->>FE: 200 { score, level, breakdown, top_tips, can_message }
        alt can_message == true
            FE-->>User: Show "Ready to message!" badge + full breakdown
        else can_message == false
            FE-->>User: Show warning + top_tips to improve profile
        end
    end
```

