## 7. Component Architecture

```mermaid
classDiagram
    class app_py {
        +GET /api/outreach/readiness
        +POST /api/outreach/generate
        -db : data module
        -outreach_module : outreach.py
    }

    class outreach_py {
        +generate_outreach_message(sender, recipient, context) dict
        +compute_outreach_readiness(user) dict
        -_call_ai(prompt) str
        -_first_name(full_name) str
        -_TONE_OPENERS dict
        -_TONE_CLOSERS dict
        -_OUTREACH_CHECKS list
    }

    class data_users_py {
        +CURRENT_USER dict
        +USERS list
        +get_user_by_id(user_id) dict
    }

    class api_js {
        +generateOutreachMessage(recipientId, tone, goal, customNote) Promise
        +getOutreachReadiness(userId) Promise
    }

    app_py --> outreach_py : calls
    app_py --> data_users_py : reads
    api_js --> app_py : HTTP JSON
```

